com.planbase.pdf.layoutmanager.pages

Class SinglePage

  • com.planbase.pdf.layoutmanager.pages.SinglePage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RenderTarget

    public class SinglePage
implements RenderTarget

    Caches the contents of a specific, single page for later drawing. Inner classes are what's added to the cache and what controls the drawing. You generally want to use class PageGrouping when you want automatic page-breaking. SinglePage is for when you want to force something onto a specific page only.

    See Also:
    class PageGrouping
